'''2015年[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]'''（{{lang-en|'''2015 MTV Movie Awards'''}}）于2015年4月12日在[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[诺基亚剧院|诺基亚剧院]]举行。喜剧演员、作家[[艾米·舒默|艾米·舒默]]担任主持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2022926/amy-schumer-2015-mtv-movie-awards-host/|title=Amy Schumer Announced She Was Hosting The 2015 MTV Movie Awards In The Best Way Possible|date=10 December 2014|work=MTV.com|accessdate=12 December 2014|archive-date=2015-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502125839/http://www.mtv.com/news/2022926/amy-schumer-2015-mtv-movie-awards-host/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。颁奖礼的全新标志由澳大利亚夫妻档艺术家Dabs Myla设计<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2089294/mtv-movie-awards-logo-dabs-myla/|title=Dabs Myla Announced They Are Designing The 2015 MTV Movie Awards|date=25 February 2015|work=MTV.com|accessdate=25 February 2015|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510034212/http://www.mtv.com/news/2089294/mtv-movie-awards-logo-dabs-myla/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，舞台布景亦由二人完成。[[凯莉·奥斯本|凯莉·奥斯本]]、乔什·霍洛维茨、克里斯蒂娜·加里波第和英国歌手[[洁西·J|洁西·J]]主持暖场秀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/watch-amy-schumer-rip-hollywood-a-new-one-at-mtv-movie-awards-20150412|title=Watch Amy Schumer Rip Hollywood a New One at MTV Movie Awards|date=12 April 2015|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=13 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430021627/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/watch-amy-schumer-rip-hollywood-a-new-one-at-mtv-movie-awards-20150412|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/mtv-movie-awards-highlights-shailene-woodley-fault-in-our-stars-1201471134/|title= Shailene Woodley, ‘Fault in Our Stars’ Dominate at MTV Movie Awards|date= 12 April 2015|work= Variety|accessdate= 13 April 2015|archive-date= 2015-05-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150504194416/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/mtv-movie-awards-highlights-shailene-woodley-fault-in-our-stars-1201471134/|dead-url= no}}</